<div><head>丹陽記</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1686_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1686_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1686_CHANT_001-1a.2">江寧縣南三十里有慈母山，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1686_CHANT_001-1a.3">積石臨江，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1686_CHANT_001-1a.4">生簫管竹。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1686_CHANT_001-1a.5">昔伶倫采竹嶰谷，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1686_CHANT_001-1a.6">其後惟此簳見珍，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1686_CHANT_001-1a.7">故歷代常給樂府，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1686_CHANT_001-1a.8">而俗呼鼓吹山，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1686_CHANT_001-1a.9">今慈湖戍常㮏采之。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1686_CHANT_001-1a.10">王褒《洞簫》即稱此也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1686_CHANT_001-1a.11">其竹圓緻，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1686_CHANT_001-1a.12">異於眾處。<lb/></seg>
</p>
